The subclass can refer its immediate super class by using super keyword.

3 ways to use super :-

#constructor
1)To refer superclass constructor in subclass
2)1st statement in the subclass constructor
3)Constructors can be referred only from other constructor
  eg) super(parameters)/super();
  
 #method
 1)To refer superclass method in subclass
 2)1st statement in the subclass constructor
 eg) super.method_name();
 
 #variable
 1)To refer super class instance variable from sub class
 eg) super.variable_name=variable_name;